  "2026-02-21T14:11:41.220Z",maintainer-agent,"Evidence: ran pm test pm-06t --run --timeout 3600 --json (all 4 linked checks passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage, node scripts/run-tests.mjs test, focused close-command test slice, pnpm build). Coverage gate remained green under the enforced 100% thresholds. Regression sweeps passed: pm test-all --status in_progress --timeout 3600 --json => items=11 linked_tests=62 passed=36 failed=0 skipped=26; pm test-all --status closed --timeout 3600 --json => items=21 linked_tests=57 passed=20 failed=0 skipped=37. Follow-up items created: none."
